    <title>2022-9-27，leetcode每日一题</title>
    <link href="https://kimilancet.github.io/2022/09/28/leetcode_206/"/>
    <id>https://kimilancet.github.io/2022/09/28/leetcode_206/</id>
    <published>2022-09-28T12:06:45.389Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-28T12:06:27.526Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>原题链接：<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/reverse-linked-list/">https://leetcode.cn/problems/reverse-linked-list/</a></p><h2 id="题目大意"><a href="#题目大意" class="headerlink" title="题目大意"></a>题目大意</h2><p>给你单链表的头节点，反转链表，并返回反转后的链表。</p><h2 id="题意分析"><a href="#题意分析" class="headerlink" title="题意分析"></a>题意分析</h2><p>设原链表为</p><p>1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;NULL（此时1为head）</p><p>则反转之后的链表为</p><p>3-&gt;2-&gt;1-&gt;NULL</p><p>换个方向看看</p><p>NULL&lt;-1&lt;-2&lt;-3（此时3为head）</p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">ListNode* <span class="title">reverseList</span><span class="params">(ListNode* head)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        ListNode* last=<span class="literal">nullptr</span>;<span class="comment">//last为双指针中的前一个指针</span></span><br><span class="line">        ListNode* curr=head;<span class="comment">//curr为双指针中的后一个指针，初始位置在头结点</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(curr!=<span class="literal">nullptr</span>)&#123;<span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line">            ListNode* keep=curr-&gt;next;<span class="comment">//定义一个keep指针，保存当前结点的next</span></span><br><span class="line">            curr-&gt;next=last;<span class="comment">//将当前结点的next反向为前一个结点，改变链表指向</span></span><br><span class="line">            last=curr;<span class="comment">//将last指针向后移动</span></span><br><span class="line">            curr=keep;<span class="comment">//将curr指针向后移动</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> last;<span class="comment">//返回last指针</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="解释"><a href="#解释" class="headerlink" title="解释"></a>解释</h2><p>我们可以将原链表的指向理解为从左往右，而反转之后的链表看作是从右往左，而第7行代码就进行了反向操作；退出循环的条件为curr指针到达相当于原链表中NULL的位置，那么last作为curr前面的一个指针，这时到达了原链表中3的位置，而前面的1，2结点都进行了反向操作，这时的指向应该是1&lt;-2&lt;-3，所以我们只需要返回到达了原链表3的位置的last指针就返回了反转后的链表。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
